Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory and excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee, O Lord, most high.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With those words, we set the energy for the group
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all of us forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if it's forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, we set the energy for our future forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Forevermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, having taken care of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,now we'll have to turn our attention to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, today is a wondrous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have all our friends from Korea and Dr. Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello, Dr. Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the head of the Radhaswami Retreat Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have it correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Radhaswami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows if she says no, she gets a blow, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we went to Korea for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dr. Moon took care of us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a wondrous trip and spoke via translator there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we will speak in both English and Korean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people here are from Korea?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Korea because I've been there twice, so it'll be somewhat unique today, very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Korean people were extremely hospitable to us when we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember, if you're a spiritual teacher, you're treated somewhat differently in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because I said, gee, I don't have any Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the word that I didn't have any Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six people spread out over the whole big city of Seoul and searched the entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And by God, in a warehouse somewhere, they found some Diet Pepsi in the back of this warehouse and brought it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the day was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six people searching for a Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the reverence with which they hold a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt very honored by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-six people searched for a Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also learned never to appreciate anything because if you hesitate and appreciate by something,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to go and buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I looked at a Buddha, and, you know, it was an antique Buddha, and it was a beautiful Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at it like, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I walked away, and I noticed Dr. Moon is dickering with the owner of the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to spend $6.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to spend $6,000 for this antique Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I learned never look like you'll appreciate something because they're going to have to get it for you, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was the style of life there and the way they greet each other, you know, in such a genteel culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get spoiled being in such a genteel culture and coming back to one that is really far more crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh...
