Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable what goes on in the public domain nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, start, we will first present what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have a translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, my name is Daho Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daho Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Daho Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Daho means, uh, large lake, great lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so today will be a little different than usual, which means it will be the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When do I start translating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That shows your silly, silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we prepared to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go through the presentation of the material to cover the basics,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the most important things that I want you to be sure to know and be familiar with will become second nature to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first slide we have is always the scale of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which today we...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have in both English and Korean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're ready for that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it took me quite a while to write this part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me quite a while to write this part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's legible from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you can see, on the left, we have the scale of consciousness in English,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the right, we have it in Korean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it's a guide to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the left, it's in Korean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this one right here is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be over a little bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were in Korea, the people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were in Korea, the people were extremely gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you go to Korea too often, you get spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you come back to the States, you're upset because people are not bowing to you when you meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So their culture has a certain graciousness to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Graciousness that is lacking in many other cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why Korea has always had a special place in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So even when you walk by a stranger, they go like so, like in a hotel lobby, you know, you meet somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the strangers all greet each other thusly. Isn't that beautiful? A way to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a need to the Korean culture, a charm, a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A charm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Charm, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need to import a lot of Korean people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To teach America the graciousness of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, to offset the aggressiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, without the grace, the aggressiveness becomes imbalanced, it becomes overly aggressive, and the ship falls over this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and Korea is very successful because it also is assertive and, you know, it's not wishy-washy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So this doesn't mean wishy-washy, just says you better be careful because God will get you if you don't.
