Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it into Korean. I think almost all of them are translated by now, and if not, they will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,be. So, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,거의 모든 책이 한국말로 번역된 것으로 알고 있습니다. 아마 안 된
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,것들은 곧 될 것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're very happy. We're very happy that the books are available to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,우리는 한국인들에게 한국어로 책이 전해지고 있다는 것이 매우 행복합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will present a sequence of slides that covers the basics, and then the presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,will be translated into Korean right away. So you won't have to wait for the Korean
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,translation. It will follow immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,기본적인 것들을 커버하기 위해서 계속 시리즈의 슬라이드를 보여드릴 것이고
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,한국말로 바로 트랜슬레이션 해드리겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So here, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to slide number one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,첫 번째 슬라이드를 보겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not number one, but the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the slide lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, I've got them circled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever one, they're circled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go through the circled list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,동그라미로 표시된 것부터 해주십시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the map of consciousness in English, and you see it combines the way you view
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God, the way you view yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that determines how you experience life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It determines what emotions tend to predominate, and then we give it, in terms of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,research, the name of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see that the enlightened states begin with honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They really begin with honesty, and that moves up to trust, and then optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot the translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, we'll get around to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the map of consciousness in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,On the right, you see how you view God, and how you view yourself, and the levels that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,suit you, and how emotions are expressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And those are the things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need to really calculate that you know who you are and what can affect what
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So despite the fact that there are a number of new words being read or exa illustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,on the wide screen on the website, you'll never know that you're going to be a hero if
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody got caught up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to do them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question was what you actually think about self, about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're supposed to see something from the gears because there's nothing to get behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person, when they're born, is born with a certain level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Each person already has a calibrated level of consciousness at the moment of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that brings in the whole subject of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And Westerners tend to think of karma as an Eastern philosophic position
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and not an experiential reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness research, however, shows that it is an important fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact. It's not just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness research is not just a theory. It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that karma is extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole purpose of human life is to undo negative karma and acquire positive karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the most important thing in human life is to get rid of negative karma and get positive karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If the arm says it's true, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I refer to her as the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When you want to see if a thing is true or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she merely holds out her arm and I press down with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I press down moderately. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If what I'm holding in mind is true, her arm goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is false, her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the reaction of protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is pro-life. Pro-life supports life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And falsehood is that which is anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is a primitive reaction that starts way back at the level of protozoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's built into the proto-planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If primitive life could not discern good from bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if primitive life could not discern good from bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it would soon die of poisoning itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing an organism needs to know is this good
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and supports life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it bad and will kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing to know is this good and supports life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it bad and will kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the first thing to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So this response is inborn, right from the level of protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,onto human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The reaction to this truth is inborn to the protozoa as well as to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's built because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the expressions of life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are expressions of levels of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that's too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's built into the infinite field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the human,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this is individual consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all share one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals all share one consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And humans have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,individual consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what one bird knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what one bird knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all the birds know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,explanations for this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomenon of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth makes your arm go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Falsehood makes your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth makes your arm go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And falsehood makes your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many explanations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for this reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens if you believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you believe in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then your arm will go strong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and weak with falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you deny God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're an atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and deny God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this will not work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those who deny
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are denied the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,benefit of knowing the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to do this test,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you need two people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that are integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people that themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you need more than 200 people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,who are of a full level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, after we wrote about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,there were various professors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,professors at universities and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who said it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after we wrote about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there were various professors, professors at universities and all, who said it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after we wrote about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there were various professors, professors at universities and all, who said it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When we did our research,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there many professors over at the university
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and people like that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,claimed that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,this doesn't actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all atheists.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are all atheists.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that we find themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as Repul Champs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They had really popular names there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Popular names
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tell atheists
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,don't bother
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't work for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the source of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you deny divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically you would not be entitled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fruits, the benefits of knowing truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:23:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so when we say glory and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,excelsis Deo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we signify that God
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is sovereign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,by that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we then are able to use
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,this system
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so the road to salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,traverses the road
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the road of salvation
