Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.31,0:26:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.42,0:26:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I attended a lecture on kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was showing the staff of my clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,how to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.55,0:27:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in an exercise class
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.26,0:27:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was showing to my students
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.78,0:27:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,how to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.99,0:27:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was showing to my students
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.60,0:27:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.65,0:27:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to our hospital staff to show how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.85,0:27:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When people look at fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,just looking at the light makes their arm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was demonstrating this to the staff of the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.27,0:28:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted a couple of volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, we had a group that was working on the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.81,0:28:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were trying to cure various diseases at the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.81,0:28:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And some of their students on the Course in Miracles were standing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.14,0:28:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, come along with me, I just want to show something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.52,0:28:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I took a couple of the students with me to do this test in front of my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.66,0:28:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited a few students.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.66,0:28:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited a few students who were doing miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.66,0:28:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said to the students, now look at this fluorescent light.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.69,0:28:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So they looked at the fluorescent light like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.51,0:28:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I pressed down on their arm, and they did not go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.13,0:29:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And they said, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.42,0:29:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.42,0:29:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.42,0:29:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All these other people, their arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.42,0:29:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But these people, their arm does not go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.85,0:29:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I found that spiritual orientation changes your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual person does not go weak when they look at fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual person does not go weak when they look at fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.04,0:29:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.29,0:30:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your physical response to stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.80,0:30:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your physical response to stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.80,0:30:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your whole energy balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual orientation changes your energy balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So to do the research further,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.66,0:30:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some students who were starting the Course of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.29,0:30:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Students.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had five or six. I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.29,0:30:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.98,0:30:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They looked at the fluorescent light
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.44,0:30:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.79,0:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just starting the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.29,0:31:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, you know, the Course in Miracles
