Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.56,0:31:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, oh, every week or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.96,0:31:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I retested this group of students
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.72,0:31:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who were starting the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.22,0:31:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,every week or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.46,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the new students
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,always went weak to the fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.30,0:31:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I tested them every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And every week, they went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.75,0:31:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They went, every week, they went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.15,0:32:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, around Lesson 70,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.54,0:32:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about the 70th day of a Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesson 70, about the 70th day,
