Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried it at home and proved it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.28,0:32:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.41,0:32:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that led to the research
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.00,0:32:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrating myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.25,0:32:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And it led eventually to the map that you see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:32:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.25,0:33:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
