Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.03,0:34:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.13,0:34:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.82,0:34:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.86,0:34:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.32,0:34:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's useful as a research tool.
