Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.69,0:34:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.59,0:34:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very useful as a research tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.19,0:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a clinical fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.86,0:34:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a clinical fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the theory of why it works
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.07,0:34:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is variable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.73,0:34:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really not understandable
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.13,0:34:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get to the field of quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.42,0:35:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Advanced theoretical physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.82,0:35:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really not understandable until you get to the field of quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.46,0:35:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I will ask her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.09,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
