Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.05,0:35:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200 resistors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.07,0:35:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200 resistors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.15,0:35:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200 resistors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.84,0:35:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200 resistors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.21,0:35:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.67,0:35:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She went weak with...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.17,0:35:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I held Adolf Hitler in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.38,0:35:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,she goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.13,0:35:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold a picture of Adolf Hitler,
