Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.21,0:35:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what he calibrated at,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.73,0:35:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,70 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.51,0:35:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I held a picture of Adolf Hitler in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.90,0:35:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan's arm became weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.30,0:36:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Adolf Hitler is estimated to be 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.75,0:36:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.19,0:36:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,she does not know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.13,0:36:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.55,0:36:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan does not know what I'm thinking in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.23,0:36:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.11,0:36:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,via energy dynamics,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.73,0:36:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we are connected in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.34,0:36:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For whatever reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.80,0:36:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan and I are connected
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.94,0:36:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,by the energy dynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.36,0:36:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I'm holding in mind affects her response,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.61,0:36:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and she doesn't even know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.51,0:36:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't know what I'm thinking in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm thinking in my head is,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.01,0:36:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is affected by sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.44,0:36:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also directly connected to Susan's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.03,0:36:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're addressing the infinite field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.17,0:36:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to say something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.15,0:37:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness has no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.76,0:37:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is outside of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet includes all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thisクール formidable
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.01,0:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is outside of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.40,0:37:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,while it includes all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is outside of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.88,0:37:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the field of energy, because the field of energy of consciousness, the energy, has no beginning or no end. It has no middle.
