Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.90,0:49:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.23,0:49:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No attractions,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.30,0:49:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.15,0:50:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever wins the election,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.11,0:50:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.17,0:50:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's okay either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.59,0:50:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The country will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.38,0:50:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.57,0:50:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we move up a little higher to willingness, which is more optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.11,0:50:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we work up to acceptance, which is based on forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.67,0:50:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Course of Miracles, here's the power of the Course of Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.53,0:50:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to forgive everything and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.30,0:50:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you're willing to forgive everything and anyone, the world begins to look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.19,0:51:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it opens the way, eventually, for reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.65,0:51:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is why I like the Korean lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.07,0:51:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go like so, you're showing reverence for life, reverence for your fellow man,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.55,0:51:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,reverence for your creator, reverence for...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.53,0:51:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For your country. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.17,0:51:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful way to live in the world of reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.65,0:51:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you try to forgive anyone and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.11,0:51:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the world begins to look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.73,0:51:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you start to have a sense of reverence for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.15,0:51:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You start to have a sense of respect for the country and the God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.78,0:51:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You start to have a sense of respect for the country and the God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.96,0:51:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Dr. Kim, you like Korean culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.26,0:51:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you like Korean culture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.46,0:51:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you like Korean culture, because you respect each other and express your respect for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.00,0:52:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So with spiritual practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.23,0:52:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,one experiences oneself and the world differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.19,0:52:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it appears differently, it looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.80,0:52:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Through spiritual practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.63,0:52:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,people experience themselves differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.94,0:52:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and they view themselves differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.55,0:52:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.57,0:52:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially to be loving towards all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.73,0:52:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what can I do to help the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.92,0:52:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't help their own garage, but they're going to save the world, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.61,0:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.21,0:53:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to move ahead in consciousness is to be loving towards all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.26,0:53:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be as benign and loving as you can be towards all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.40,0:53:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The love is a different love.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.80,0:53:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual love is not personal and it's not an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.26,0:53:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can appreciate. One form of love is appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.59,0:54:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the people who set off bombs around the world and kill innocent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.55,0:54:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they do that out of a belief system that somehow they're serving God by doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.44,0:54:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.71,0:54:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,their brain wants to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.46,0:54:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that their job is to kill all people who don't believe the way they believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.63,0:54:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's true. They may kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.48,0:54:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, should we hate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.07,0:54:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.40,0:54:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.50,0:55:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The little lion will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.65,0:55:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the little lion loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.53,0:55:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The little lion loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.80,0:55:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the little lion will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.07,0:55:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the little lion will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.34,0:55:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, he eats you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.65,0:55:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can love even the lion that eats your cat and your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.36,0:55:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I came front to front with a cougar very recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.09,0:56:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked out my kitchen window and here was a cougar walking right past my kitchen window.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.78,0:56:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.50,0:56:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As a doggie, come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.00,0:56:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.92,0:56:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.34,0:56:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very big, uh, it's a very big cat, but it's five, six feet long.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.76,0:56:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'd be happy to eat you, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.67,0:56:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I respect the mountain lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.88,0:56:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.01,0:56:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, respect is a different kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.76,0:56:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You sonn.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.19,0:56:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, God created the cougar?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.82,0:56:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.44,0:56:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he created evolution, and evolution created the cougar.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.82,0:56:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in court, God is responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.73,0:56:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.69,0:56:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.65,0:57:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, God created Cougars, and God created shelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.21,0:57:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Cougar eats you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.90,0:57:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Cougar eats you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.53,0:57:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Cougar eats you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.13,0:57:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,not make you happy
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.23,0:57:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will make
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.11,0:57:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the cougar happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.32,0:57:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I'm careful
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.67,0:57:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when I let the dog out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.44,0:57:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I look outside first
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.69,0:57:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure there's no
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.55,0:57:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So being loving
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.57,0:57:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,does not mean being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.53,0:57:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.32,0:57:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,misunderstand
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.34,0:57:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,impersonal love
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.78,0:57:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and they think
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.53,0:57:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that they should be
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.76,0:57:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hospitable
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.90,0:57:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.03,0:57:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in their own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.84,0:58:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you have a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.75,0:58:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not wise
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.82,0:58:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to invite a cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.17,0:58:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to live in your backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.25,0:58:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.23,0:58:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we live today
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.26,0:58:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we live in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.42,0:58:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in which conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.07,0:58:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,arises
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.42,0:58:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as an impersonal
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.19,0:58:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So divine evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.30,0:59:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,results in the creation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.63,0:59:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of benign
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.71,0:59:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,friendly people
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.78,0:59:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and also
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.03,0:59:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,warlike people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.59,0:59:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So divine evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.94,0:59:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,results in the creation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.86,0:59:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of very gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.59,0:59:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and loving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.53,0:59:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.84,0:59:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there are places in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.40,0:59:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where the people believe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.26,0:59:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that to serve God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.63,0:59:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they must kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.42,0:59:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing you is serving God.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.75,0:59:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In what part of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.09,0:59:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They think that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.80,0:59:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.15,0:59:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there are whole areas
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.34,0:59:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that think
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.92,0:59:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that the way to serve God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.82,0:59:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.21,0:59:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.42,0:59:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there are places
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.42,0:59:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,where people believe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.42,0:59:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that the way to serve God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.42,0:59:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.42,1:00:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I respect
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.84,1:00:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that belief
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.67,1:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do not want
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.96,1:00:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,them living in my backyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.48,1:00:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.05,1:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.73,1:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who are also misguided
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.17,1:00:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,who think the way
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.65,1:00:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.30,1:00:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.59,1:00:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.67,1:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.17,1:00:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who think the way
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.67,1:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to invite mountain lions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.17,1:00:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to live in your backyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.21,1:00:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who are
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.86,1:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,misguided
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.53,1:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,think it is right
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.67,1:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to invite a small cat
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.05,1:00:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to your yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.42,1:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Their idea is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.50,1:00:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they will change
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.15,1:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the cougar
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.38,1:00:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who will then become
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.46,1:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.80,1:00:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.05,1:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll purify you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.92,1:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll eat you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.92,1:01:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that takes care
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.13,1:01:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the political tensions
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.71,1:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.05,1:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It only took us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.01,1:01:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.88,1:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.23,1:01:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everything be
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.42,1:01:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.03,1:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but respect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.98,1:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to respect
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.59,1:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the mountain lion
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.40,1:01:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't need
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.21,1:01:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to respect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.23,1:01:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.63,1:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to hate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.82,1:01:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.53,1:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to hate the mountain lion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.88,1:01:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also remember
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.03,1:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he will be glad
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.78,1:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.51,1:01:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.11,1:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be also
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.53,1:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,handled with
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.53,1:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.80,1:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.80,1:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be also
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.40,1:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,handled with
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.46,1:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,reason and logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.80,1:01:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So faith is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.23,1:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,bulwarked.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.32,1:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So faith is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.28,1:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,reinforced by reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.50,1:02:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So faith is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.65,1:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,reinforced by reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.88,1:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and reason
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.92,1:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,go hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.90,1:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and reason
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.73,1:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,go hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.48,1:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.98,1:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.90,1:02:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.57,1:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.50,1:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of talky talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.00,1:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.11,1:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have five minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.15,1:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? We have five minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.32,1:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.92,1:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.65,1:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything I said
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.80,1:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,simple and obvious?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.00,1:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.40,1:02:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.88,1:02:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody got any objections
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.30,1:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.80,1:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to jump up and become indignant?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.63,1:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.46,1:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.09,1:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.03,1:03:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the trick is to make God's way
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.13,1:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.57,1:03:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we have to do is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.21,1:03:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,create God's way
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.32,1:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,into our own way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.03,1:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think the way
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.46,1:03:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to do it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.01,1:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without having to go to church
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.34,1:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be gracious
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.76,1:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and loving towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.44,1:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That will save you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.51,1:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.92,1:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.42,1:03:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in life
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.50,1:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you exist,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.67,1:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to go to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.17,1:03:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.44,1:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.07,1:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to me, spiritual then means an overall attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.55,1:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.78,1:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't what you do, it isn't what you say, it isn't what you buy, it isn't what you sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.78,1:04:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, spiritual is a general attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.90,1:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way you are in the world, it's the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.23,1:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way you are is a consequence of that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.84,1:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not what you do, it's not what you say, it's what you are that changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.28,1:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I will see you after the break.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.32,1:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.59,1:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are changes the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.94,1:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we will resume, God willing.
