Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.88,1:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so there was a doubt raised about the divinity of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.68,1:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And using the scale of consciousness, this particular slide right here,
