Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.53,1:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So just as heaven and bliss and divinity is above, hell is below.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.06,1:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of, as I have described in previous lectures, in exploring the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.60,1:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it was, they were pretty much, it was a very big thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.69,1:16:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much as Dante envisioned them, Dante.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.92,1:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said in my previous lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.88,1:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of hell is very similar to what Dante described.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.30,1:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The degree of agony increases beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.73,1:16:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In the higher levels of hell, there is torture and dementia and savagery.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.23,1:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just the top of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.53,1:16:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the good part of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.46,1:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it gets serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.69,1:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kept going deeper and deeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.26,1:17:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the source of hell, the levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.81,1:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember in the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.72,1:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,passing a sign that said,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.43,1:17:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye who enter here, give up all hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.35,1:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As I went down to hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.39,1:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a sign that said,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.94,1:17:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who pass through here, give up all hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.63,1:17:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing that sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.43,1:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With some kind of incredibly, I don't know, demented dedication,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.60,1:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I proceeded to go into the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.61,1:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ignored the warning sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.89,1:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I ignored the sign and continued to go down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.44,1:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon all hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.32,1:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye who enter here, was the warning sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.56,1:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As I passed here,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.76,1:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in Dante's description of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.01,1:18:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that occurs in Dante's
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.47,1:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dante, D-A-N-T-E
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.22,1:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,description of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.85,1:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But there it was on the right side of me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.39,1:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a sign, a warning sign
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.06,1:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon all hope, ye who enter here
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.43,1:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, driven by
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.77,1:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.02,1:18:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a dedication to truth and the extreme
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.72,1:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I ignored the sign and the warning
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.31,1:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went deeper and deeper
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.35,1:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,into hell
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.67,1:19:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and reached hopelessness and despair
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.35,1:19:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and abandonment
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.39,1:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness and despair and abandonment
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.72,1:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I experienced despair forever
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.65,1:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that level of despair
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.03,1:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and that level of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.84,1:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there is agony forever
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.25,1:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that level of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.85,1:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand what forever means
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.03,1:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As I speak, it is only a word to you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.81,1:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But in hell, there is agony forever
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.18,1:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that level of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.38,1:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you experience eternity
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.77,1:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless despair forever
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.14,1:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The agony not of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.26,1:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,like the higher levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.89,1:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but of the soul
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.03,1:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at the lowest levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.69,1:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The agony not of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.72,1:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,like the higher levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.76,1:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience the pain of death
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.50,1:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The agony of death
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.30,1:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At the deepest levels of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.59,1:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there for eternity
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.35,1:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there for eternity
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.27,1:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.72,1:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Experientially
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.72,1:21:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At last a thought came from within
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.69,1:21:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God I ask Him for help
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.97,1:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an Atheist at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.18,1:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an Atheist at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.02,1:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of my life, I was a dizendo
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.10,1:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of my life, I was a denial
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.00,1:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're an atheist
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.22,1:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and find yourself pleading with God
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.68,1:21:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you've almost completed the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.75,1:21:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of the totality of eternal despair
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.14,1:22:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,agony forever
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.02,1:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,agony forever
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.64,1:22:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a voice arose from within
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.07,1:22:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and said
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.78,1:22:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.63,1:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.85,1:22:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of eternal pain
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.01,1:22:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the midst of the whole of pain
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.43,1:22:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.25,1:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.96,1:22:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the voice that came up from within me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.56,1:22:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an archangel that heard me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.68,1:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That archangel
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.84,1:22:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 6,000
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.65,1:22:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,an archangel
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.53,1:22:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,at calibration level 6,000
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.52,1:22:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,heard me
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.39,1:22:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and must have given me a glance
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.84,1:22:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be noticed
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.02,1:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by an archangel
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.10,1:23:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,completely took me out of the depths of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.19,1:23:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I went into a state
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.40,1:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of eternal ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.13,1:23:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.05,1:23:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,revealed itself as divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.22,1:23:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by looking at the archangel
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.05,1:23:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.98,1:23:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and as a state of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.31,1:23:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced everything that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.18,1:23:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as a peace of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.52,1:23:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That all exists
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.64,1:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.18,1:23:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and infinitely perfect and beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.22,1:23:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,revealed itself
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.27,1:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in a profound and stunning way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.03,1:23:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists is God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.77,1:23:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that exists is God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.07,1:23:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's calibrate that extreme.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.38,1:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to pay attention to the actual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.73,1:23:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to cover yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.38,1:23:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can see what God created
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.68,1:23:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's all by God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.47,1:23:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can saw goodness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.50,1:23:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's all beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.60,1:23:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because he created me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.57,1:23:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and to speak about his all.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.10,1:23:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything comes from God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.22,1:23:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and God created me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.50,1:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and he created you
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.26,1:23:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and said let's go around in that world
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.11,1:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's impossible to be normal
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.18,1:24:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't lack 141
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.61,1:24:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't lack 253
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.51,1:24:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if you allow God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.35,1:24:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that human physical spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.52,1:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,return joy and then then
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.06,1:24:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,kpq 2g two of you guys are telling me
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.44,1:24:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the confirmation of the highest levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.21,1:24:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,God manifests as divinity creator.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.72,1:24:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond creator, God is unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.52,1:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Godhead, out of the Godhead arises God, the creator.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.39,1:24:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the light shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.57,1:24:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of the light of God arose all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.00,1:24:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All of creation arose in what is called the light of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.93,1:24:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the light of God is just...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.00,1:24:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.02,1:25:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of creation arose from what is biblically called the light of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.18,1:25:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.69,1:25:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All creation arises from what is described as the light of God in the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.98,1:25:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the light of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.27,1:25:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of God is consciousness, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.57,1:25:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So the light of God is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.72,1:25:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of us, all of us are conscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.78,1:25:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, we all experience the light of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.42,1:25:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To know that you are, that you exist, is a divine revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.89,1:25:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To know that you exist, is a divine revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.51,1:26:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We take it for granted.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.55,1:26:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And never realize that it is a divine gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.65,1:26:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the light of God, we wouldn't even know that we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.64,1:26:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.84,1:26:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we confirm all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.42,1:26:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.93,1:26:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,truth, resist, beyond level 6,000, 7,000, 6,000, around 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.77,1:26:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we need to know anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.42,1:26:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's interesting, what I thought was interesting experientially,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.13,1:26:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it was very profound experientially,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.18,1:26:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was very transformative,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.63,1:26:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that we can literally experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.92,1:26:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,experience an archangel, even in this realm, we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.56,1:27:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was interesting to me was that the encounter with the great angel was that we can directly experience God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.44,1:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.44,1:27:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has guardian angels, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.44,1:27:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.80,1:27:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.80,1:27:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get our guardian angels out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.94,1:27:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get our guardian angels out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.51,1:27:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a reality. They're a reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.51,1:27:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.51,1:27:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.72,1:27:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The other morning I woke up out of a sound sleep and an archangel told me what to do and I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.85,1:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.85,1:27:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I got on the phone and I said, I just heard a voice telling me,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.85,1:27:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I told them what the voice told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.85,1:27:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.46,1:27:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.46,1:28:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the voice of a guardian angel that I heard, resist, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.46,1:28:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.46,1:28:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It came as a voice, not as a thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.46,1:28:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.46,1:28:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you acknowledge your guardian angels,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.46,1:28:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they become more stronger, more close to your awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.03,1:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.03,1:28:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.03,1:28:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel abandoned by God because you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.03,1:28:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.10,1:28:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.10,1:28:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.10,1:28:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.10,1:28:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.10,1:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.10,1:28:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.02,1:28:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.02,1:28:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.02,1:28:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.02,1:28:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.00,1:28:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.00,1:28:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.18,1:28:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.18,1:29:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.82,1:29:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.82,1:29:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.82,1:29:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.82,1:29:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.82,1:29:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept you alive all these years.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.02,1:29:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.75,1:29:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.97,1:29:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even below 200, those who are below 200, do they have guardian angels?
