Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.78,1:37:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서 생명이 존재하기 위해서는
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.78,1:38:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,어떤 것이 독이고 어떤 것이 음식인지를
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.78,1:38:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,구별하는 어떠한 방법을 알고 있어야만 합니다
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.78,1:38:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,구별하는 어떠한 방법을 알고 있어야만 합니다
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.81,1:38:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the evolution over the millennia
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.81,1:38:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the representation of the different levels
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.81,1:38:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.81,1:38:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,starting out with bacteria and worms and fish and octopus
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.30,1:38:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the octopus
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.30,1:38:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you get up to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.30,1:38:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the snake and the alligator
