Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.13,1:38:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinosaur 공룡은 60으로 측정됩니다
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.09,1:38:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not very good eating dinosaurs
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.09,1:38:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,먹기에는 좋지 않습니다 공룡은
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.23,1:38:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we come up through the mice and the rats
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.23,1:38:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to the rhinoceros
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.39,1:38:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who's not very friendly
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.39,1:38:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to the songbirds
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.76,1:38:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's the dove
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.01,1:39:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the polar bear is pretty intelligent
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.01,1:39:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and so is the grizzly bear
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.19,1:39:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's the water buffalo
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.19,1:39:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,here's the black bear
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.19,1:39:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the jackal, the fox, the wolf
