Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.84,1:39:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we come to javelina
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.55,1:39:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see we're below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.77,1:39:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to ignore these people
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.60,1:39:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because the hippopotamus kills more people
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.60,1:39:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think than any other animal right now
