Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.60,1:39:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so below 200 you're in danger
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.60,1:39:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At 200 and up now you begin to see
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.76,1:39:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of that which is benign
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.76,1:39:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is voracious
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.98,1:39:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Voracious, the dinosaur is voracious
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.98,1:39:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And now at 200 suddenly you see a shift of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.07,1:39:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find those that stay alive by grazing
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.07,1:39:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You find the deer doesn't have to kill anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.07,1:39:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The bison doesn't kill anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.07,1:39:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They all eat grass
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.07,1:40:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody here eats grass
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.07,1:40:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When in doubt eat grass
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.19,1:40:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200 there are animals that are very dangerous to humans
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.19,1:40:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and above 200 there are herbivorous animals
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.19,1:40:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we move up the scale of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.19,1:40:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it's represented in the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.19,1:40:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the sheep are at 210
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.19,1:40:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Range cattle 210
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.19,1:40:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The elephant at 235
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.23,1:40:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The elephant is relatively safe unless you cross him
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.77,1:40:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he may squish you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.77,1:40:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you come to the farm horse
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.23,1:40:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the domestic cat 245
