Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.48,1:40:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the race horses and dogs at 250
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.48,1:40:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The family dog
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.56,1:40:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kelsey our family dog calibrates at 255
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.10,1:41:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,255 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.52,1:41:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,256
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.52,1:41:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,255
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.52,1:41:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,256
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.52,1:41:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we better send her back to school
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.52,1:41:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog you're raising, Kelsey, is 265
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.52,1:41:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being loving and around humans
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.52,1:41:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The family dog will calibrate five points higher than a dog not with the family
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.52,1:41:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we get up to the gorilla at 275
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.52,1:41:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these gorillas are very famous
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.52,1:41:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Very famous gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.52,1:41:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember there was a baby dropped into a pit where the gorilla lived
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.18,1:41:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby dropped over the edge
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.18,1:41:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the gorilla came over and picked up the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.18,1:41:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the gorilla came over and picked up the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.18,1:41:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the gorilla came over and picked up the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.18,1:41:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And picked up the baby and brought it over
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.18,1:42:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And laid it gently by the gate
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.18,1:42:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For the mother to come and get it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.18,1:42:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong to the gorilla foundation
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.38,1:42:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong to the gorilla foundation?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.38,1:42:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That gorilla calibrated over 280, 290, 300
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.43,1:42:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,295, 300
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.72,1:42:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of that gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.72,1:42:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget her name
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.72,1:42:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She calibrates at 295
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.72,1:42:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,295
