Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.96,1:42:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.96,1:42:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She learns sign language
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.96,1:42:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a picture of her
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.96,1:42:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're holding a kitten
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.05,1:43:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And Coco is saying nice nice soft soft cat cat
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.39,1:43:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco the gorilla is saying nice nice soft soft cat cat
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.39,1:43:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice nice soft soft cat cat
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.78,1:43:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how you begin to love the animals
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.78,1:43:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As you yourself evolve
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.78,1:43:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You eventually love all these animals
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.78,1:43:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to love them
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.78,1:43:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the gorilla
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.78,1:43:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the gorilla is caring for a child like its own, or a gorilla has a kitten.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.94,1:43:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice, soft, soft, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.44,1:43:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a picture of the gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.32,1:43:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget her name.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.78,1:43:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got the kitty there, and she says, nice, nice, soft, soft, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.36,1:43:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice, soft, soft, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.14,1:43:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the famous cat, Oscar, who can tell when you're going to die within a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.59,1:44:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was famous in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.17,1:44:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Oscar climbs in bed with you, it means you'll be dead within a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.39,1:44:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He was correct 23 out of 24 times, or no, 23 times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.72,1:44:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was 23 times, all of them were correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.55,1:44:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the famous Alex, the gray parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.07,1:44:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a gray parrot at home, and very talky.
