Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.71,1:44:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.67,1:44:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a parrot name, Broccoli, which means very talkative.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.64,1:44:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate Broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.64,1:44:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli is over 400, 405, 402.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.13,1:44:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we have an African gray parrot at home that was a gift from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.13,1:44:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And she talks up a storm, talks to the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.13,1:45:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.39,1:45:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.07,1:45:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So the bird will say, Kelsey, Kelsey, come here, come here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.34,1:45:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the dog runs over.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.81,1:45:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In a jealous way, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.81,1:45:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Imitating your voice, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.02,1:45:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In my voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.92,1:45:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she goes, the dog runs over.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.27,1:45:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog runs over, and then she goes, get away from that bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.32,1:45:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.75,1:46:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how as they come up, we begin to relate to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.85,1:46:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to love the animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.71,1:46:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think one of the best presents you can give a kid is a kitty or a puppy or something to be responsible for.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.59,1:46:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we begin to love the animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.17,1:46:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're up in 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.51,1:46:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you love the deer, we love the elk and the deer.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.43,1:46:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you get up higher, and you really finally reach Coco, the trained gorilla, is at 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.36,1:46:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize you're safer in a cage with this gorilla than you are with about 90% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.77,1:46:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we're all like this gorilla is safer than being with 95%, 85% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.34,1:46:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safer.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.51,1:46:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we come up to the songbird's song, and then very profoundly, the cat's purr, 500, the dog's wagging tail, 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.38,1:47:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,굉장히 심오하게도 고양이의 가라랑거리는 소리와 개의 꼬리 흔들기는 500으로 측정됩니다.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.22,1:47:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So people say, well, you just imagine that the dog loves you, or that the kitty loves you,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.42,1:47:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we calibrate it and the kitty's purring, that's 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.85,1:47:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not our imagination. The kitty is loving you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.57,1:47:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,당신은 개가 당신을 사랑한다고 상상하지만 실제로
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.38,1:47:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dog's wagging tail is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.52,1:47:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,개는 실제로 당신을 사랑합니다. 왜냐하면 개의 꼬리 흔들기가 500으로, 사랑의 수준은 500으로 측정되기 때문입니다.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.81,1:47:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There was some advertiser that recently discovered that by putting a dog's wagging tail in their advertisement on television, they quadruple their sales.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.71,1:47:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,광고에 꼬리 흔드는 개의 사진을
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.63,1:47:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,광고에 꼬리 흔드는 개의 사진을
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.10,1:47:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,올려서 판매가 3배로 올랐답니다.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.64,1:47:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're having trouble with somebody in your life, try wagging your tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.65,1:48:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,당신이 살면서 누구와 문제가 있다면 당신의 꼬리를 살짝 흔들어 주세요.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.50,1:48:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.93,1:48:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a little more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.27,1:48:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,이거는 조금 더 복잡한 것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.21,1:48:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In every situation, there is...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.68,1:48:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the content and there's an infinite field and approximate field.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.60,1:48:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is local and this is overall.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.32,1:48:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,어떤 상황에도 콘텐츠가 있고 무한한 장과 근접한, 조금 더 근접한 장이 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.34,1:48:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So a definable truth has to be defined in what situation and under what circumstances a certain thing is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.98,1:48:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So a definable truth has to be defined in what situation and under what circumstances a certain thing is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.47,1:49:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to distinguish between two events, it is important to know the context and the situation in which the event takes place.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.39,1:49:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the universe is in a state of infinite potentiality, and then through the Heisenberg process, by our intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.09,1:49:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we collapse the wave function, and that which is potential becomes infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.81,1:50:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the great discovery was that human consciousness, that intention, can make things manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.19,1:50:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you have potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.89,1:50:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now by our intention, by our free will, we make them actually happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.22,1:50:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's the basis of the test that we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.56,1:50:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she does not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.53,1:51:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She does not know what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.76,1:51:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She had no way to know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.50,1:51:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no possible linear explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.30,1:51:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens is that we collapse the wave function.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.07,1:51:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say what I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.93,1:51:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not a fact, it has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.15,1:51:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it has no reality, it cannot cause your arm to go strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.73,1:51:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hold in mind, yeah.
